name: Breathing House
description: Rendered in procreate, this surreal Breathing House is a comment on housing as a basic human right. We need space to think, rest, enjoy, and take care of ourselves. This edition is the first of many Breathing Houses with proceeds going to develop a housing project in Oakland California that will help to house our shelterless. Created by street artist Bud Snow.
